**Males**  
$dS_m = -\lambda_m N_{sm}+(1-\omega_m) N_m +\delta N_{im} - \mu N_{sm}$
  
$dI_m = \lambda_m N_{vm} (1-\psi)+(\lambda_m N_{sm}) N_m -\delta N_{im} - \mu N_{im}$
  
$dV_m = -\lambda_m N_{vm} (1-\psi)+(\omega_m \mu N_{m}) - \mu N_{vm}$
  
**Females**  
$dS_f = -\lambda_f N_{sf}+(1-\omega_f) N_f +\delta N_{if} - \mu N_{sf}$
  
$dI_f = \lambda_f N_{vf} (1-\psi)+(\lambda_f N_{sf}) N_f -\delta N_{if} - \mu N_{if}$
  
$dV_f = -\lambda_f N_{vf} (1-\psi)+(\omega_f \mu N_{f}) - \mu N_{vf}$




## Updated Differential Equations

**Males**
Susceptible unexposed (11-18 yrs old):
$$\frac{dS_{m,ue}}{dt} = 0.5 \cdot (1 - \omega_m \cdot \chi) \cdot \nu \cdot n - \text{age}_{\text{in}} \cdot S_{m,ue} - \mu_{ue} \cdot S_{m,ue}$$

Susceptible exposed (18+, proxy for sexually active):
$$\frac{dS_{m,e}}{dt} = \text{age}_{\text{in}} \cdot S_{m,ue} - \mu \cdot S_{m,e} - \text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot S_{m,e} - \lambda_{m,s} \cdot \zeta_s \cdot S_{m,e} - \lambda_{m,s} \cdot (1 - \zeta_s) \cdot S_{m,e} + \delta_{s,a} \cdot I_{m,a} + \delta_{s,s} \cdot I_{m,s} - \kappa \cdot S_{m,e}$$

Infected asymptomatic:
$$\frac{dI_{m,a}}{dt} = -\text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot I_{m,a} - \mu \cdot I_{m,a} + \lambda_{m,s} \cdot (1 - \zeta_s) \cdot S_{m,e} - \delta_{s,a} \cdot I_{m,a}$$

Infected symptomatic:
$$\frac{dI_{m,s}}{dt} = -\text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot I_{m,s} - \mu \cdot I_{m,s} + \lambda_{m,s} \cdot \zeta_s \cdot S_{m,e} - \delta_{s,s} \cdot I_{m,s}$$

**Males: Vaccinated**
Vaccinated unexposed:
$$\frac{dV_{m,ue}}{dt} = 0.5 \cdot \omega_m \cdot \chi \cdot \nu \cdot n - \text{age}_{\text{in}} \cdot V_{m,ue} - \mu_{ue} \cdot V_{m,ue}$$

Vaccinated exposed/sexually active:
$$\frac{dV_{m,e}}{dt} = \text{age}_{\text{in}} \cdot V_{m,ue} - \text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot V_{m,e} - \mu \cdot V_{m,e} - \lambda_{m,v} \cdot \zeta_v \cdot V_{m,e} - \lambda_{m,v} \cdot (1 - \zeta_v) \cdot V_{m,e} + \delta_{v,a} \cdot I_{m,a} + \delta_{v,s} \cdot I_{m,s} + \kappa \cdot S_{m,e}$$

Infected asymptomatic:
$$\frac{dI_{m,v,a}}{dt} = -\text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot I_{m,v,a} - \mu \cdot I_{m,v,a} + \lambda_{m,v} \cdot (1 - \zeta_v) \cdot V_{m,e} - \delta_{v,a} \cdot I_{m,v,a}$$

Infected symptomatic:
$$\frac{dI_{m,v,s}}{dt} = -\text{age}_{\text{out}} \cdot I_{m,v,s} - \mu \cdot I_{m,v,s} + \lambda_{m,v} \cdot \zeta_v \cdot V_{m,e} - \delta_{v,s} \cdot I_{m,v,s}$$
